snippet.title: Grey Eminence - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Spanning from 1356 to 1956, steer the fate of any country on Earth through six epic centuries of conflict. Diplomacy, economics, warfare and intrigue are all weapons in your arsenal to transform the world that was into the world that could be.

Built using Unity's revolutionary Data-Oriented Tech Stack (DOTS), Grey Eminence simulates Earth on an unparalleled scale: a world with over 1,000,000 tiles, a realistic demographics model, and a logistics-based economy driven by supply & demand.

Interested in seeing Grey Eminence come to life? Support the Nestinars on Patreon: https://patreon.com/nestinars

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1858700/Grey_Eminence/
Subscribe to our newsletter: https://nestinars.com/#subscribe
